---
import Petals from './petalsFront.astro'
import Form from './form.astro'
import Comments from './comments.astro'
---
<div id="petals-container" class="op0">
  <Petals/>
</div>

<img class="top-flower" src="/images/decor-page-bottom.png" alt="">
<div id="hero" class="op0">
  <div id="hero-title" class="">
    <h2>
      Undangan<div>Pernikahan</div>
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div id="hero-img">
    <img class="hero-img" src="/images/hero.png" alt="hero">
    <img class="decor-hero op0" src="/images/decor-hero.png" alt="">
  </div>
  <p>Nabila <span>&</span> Fauzi</p>
  <p class="subhero">Uncle D Space<br>21 | 12 | 24</p>
</div>

<img class="" src="/images/devider-h2.png" alt="">

<div id="hero-ayat" class="">
  <span class="">Qs. Ar-Rum 21</span>
  <br>
  "Di antara tanda-tanda (kebesaran)-Nya ialah bahwa Dia menciptakan pasangan-pasangan untukmu dari (jenis) dirimu sendiri agar kamu merasa tenteram kepada-Nya. Dia menjadikan di antaramu rasa cinta dan kasih sayang. Sesungguhnya pada yang demikian itu benar-benar terdapat tanda-tanda (kebesaran Allah) bagi kaum yang berpikir."
</div>

<div id="c-mempelai" class="op0">
  <img class="cm-decor op0" id="cm-decor1" src="/images/flowers/stalk-yel.png" alt="">
  <img class="cm-decor op0" id="cm-decor2" src="/images/flowers/stalk-red.png" alt="">
  <div id="cm-nabila">
    <div id="cm-nabila-txt" class="">
      <h2>Nabila<div>Annisa</div></h2>
      <p class="p2">Anak pertama dari<br>Bapak Duddy Perkasa<br>dan Ibu Mia Rusmiati</p>
    </div>
    <img class="profpic" src="/images/Nabila-tr.png" alt="">
  </div>
  <div id="cm-fauzi">
    <img class="profpic" src="/images/Fauzi-tr.png" alt="">
    <div id="cm-fauzi-txt" class="">
      <h2>Fauzi<div>Irfandika</div></h2>
      <p class="p2">Anak kedua dari<br>Bapak Bakti Ramadhan<br>dan Ibu Yunyun Yuniastuti</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="c-gallery" class="op0">
  <div id="c-gallery-title" class="c-title">
    <h2><div>Pra</div> Pernikahan</h2>
    <img src="/images/decoration/praper-left.png" alt="">
  </div>
  <div id="gallery-wrapper">
    <img class="op0" width="10vw" src="/gallery/02.jpg" alt="">
    <img class="op0" width="10vw" src="/gallery/07.jpg" alt="">
    <img class="op0" width="10vw" src="/gallery/03.jpg" alt="">
    <img class="op0" width="10vw" src="/gallery/08.jpg" alt="">
    <img class="op0" width="10vw" src="/gallery/09.jpg" alt="">
    <img class="op0" width="10vw" src="/gallery/06.jpg" alt="">
    <img class="op0" width="10vw" id="gallery-mid" src="/gallery/01.jpg" alt="">
    <img class="op0" width="10vw" src="/gallery/04.jpg" alt="">
  </div>
</div>

<img class="" src="/images/devider-h2.png" alt="">

<div id="c-waktu" class="op0">
  <div id="c-waktu-title" class="op0 c-title">
    <img src="/images/decoration/rangkaian-left.png" alt="">
    <h2>Rangkaian<div>Acara</div></h2>
  </div>
  <p class="description">Rangkaian acara meliputi prosesi akad nikah dan resepsi pernikahan yang akan dilaksanakan di hari yang sama.</p>
  <div class="det-info">
    <img id="wedring" class="op0" src="/images/wedding-rings-01.svg" alt="">
    <h3>Akad Nikah</h3>
    <p>(Hanya dihadiri keluarga)</p>
  </div>
  <div class="det-info">
    <img id="wedbouq" class="op0" src="/images/wedding-bouquet-01.svg" alt="">
    <h3>Resepsi Pernikahan</h3>
    <p class=""><slot/></p>
  </div>
  <div id="ctd" class="det-info">
    <img id="hglass" class="op0" src="/images/hourglass-01.svg" alt="">
    <h3>Menuju Pernikahan</h3>
    <div id="cds"></div>
  </div>
  <button class="button" type="button"><a href="https://www.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&text=Pernikahan%20Nabila%20dan%20Fauzi&details&dates=20241221/20241221" target="_blank">Simpan Tanggal</a></button>
</div>

<img class="" src="/images/devider-h2.png" alt="">

<div id="c-tempat" class="op0">
  <div id="c-tempat-title" class="op0 c-title">
    <h2>Lokasi<div>Kegiatan</div></h2>
    <img src="/images/decoration/tempat-right.png" alt="">
  </div>
  <div id="detil-tempat" class="op0 det-info">
    <h3>Uncle D Space</h3>
    <p>Jl. Cigadung Raya Barat no. 28A<br>Cibeunying Kaler, Bandung</p>
    <img id="peta" class="op0" src="/images/map.png" alt="">
    <button class="button" type="button"><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/bWYPqw5SpdMezy2M8" target="_blank">Buka Peta</a></button>
  </div>
  <div></div>
</div>

<img class="" src="/images/devider-h2.png" alt="">

<div id="c-ucapan" class="op0">
  <h2>Ucapan<div>dan Doa</div></h2>
  <Comments server:defer/>
</div>

<div id="c-rsvp" class="op0">
  <h2>Reservasi<div>Kehadiran</div></h2>
  <Form/>
  <p id="c-rsvp-tq" class="hidden">Terima atas ucapan, doa, serta konfirmasi kehadirannya.</p>
  <img src="/images/decoration/res.png" alt="">
</div>

<img class="" src="/images/devider-h2.png" alt="">

<div id="c-hadiah" class="op0">
  <div id="c-hadiah-title" class="op0 c-title">
    <img src="/images/decoration/hadiah-left.png" alt="">
    <h2>Tanda<div>Kasih</div></h2>
  </div>
  <p>Doa, restu, serta ucapan selamat Bapak/Ibu/Saudara/i merupakan yang terpenting bagi kami. Bagi Bapak/Ibu/Saudara/i yang bermaksud memberi tanda kasih selain itu, dapat kami terima melalui:</p>
  <div id="c-hadiah-banklist" class="op0">
    Alamat:
    <div class="bank-card alamat">
      <div class="hadiah-alamat">
        <h3>Jl. Kebon Sirih Dalam no. 19</h3>
        <span>Babakan Ciamis, Sumur Bandung, Kota Bandung.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    Rekening Bank:
    <div class="bank-card card-nabila">
      <div>
        <h3>Mandiri a.n. Nabila Annisa</h3>
        <span id="bank-nabila">1310016137079</span>
      </div>
      <button id="copy-nabila" onclick="copyTextNabila()" data-copy=".bank-nabila" type="button"><img src="/images/copy.svg" alt=""></button>
    </div>
    <div class="bank-card card-fauzi">
      <div>
        <h3>BCA a.n Fauzi Irfandika</h3>
        <span id="bank-fauzi">4970646847</span>
      </div>
      <button id="copy-fauzi" onclick="copyTextFauzi()" data-copy=".bank-fauzi" type="button"><img src="/images/copy.svg" alt=""></button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p>Semoga informasi di atas dapat mempermudah Bapak/Ibu/Saudara/i dalam menyampaikan kasihnya kepada kami. Mohon dapat menghubungi kami jika bermaksud memberi tanda kasih.</p>
</div>

<img class="" src="/images/devider-h2.png" alt="">

<div id="c-penutup" class="op0">
  <h2><div>Ucapan</div>Terima Kasih</h2>
  <p>Terima kasih kami ucapkan atas perhatian, kasih sayang, serta doa dan restu Bapak/Ibu/Saudara/i, suatu kehormatan bagi kami untuk dapat mengundang anda pada hari bahagia kami. Semoga kita selalu diberkahi kesehatan dan kemampuan, agar dapat bertemu dan berkumpul tidak hanya pada hari bahagia kami, namun pada tiap kesempatan yang ada.</p>
  <div class="ttd">
    <p class="p2">tertanda<br><br><span class="ttd-kel">Keluarga</span><br><span class="ttd-nab">Nabila</span> dan <span class="ttd-fau">Fauzi</span></p>
    <img src="/images/closing.png" alt="">
  </div>
</div>

<img class="" src="/images/devider-h2.png" alt="">

<div id="c-credits" class="op0">
  <div id="creds-left">
    <p><span>Desain</span><br>Nabila dan Fauzi</p>
    <p><span>Aset Gambar</span><br>freepik.com, POLAR Photograph, Nabila dan Fauzi</p>
  </div>
  <img src="/logo_bold.svg" alt="logo">
  <div id="creds-right">
    <p><span>Website</span><br>Nabila dan Fauzi</p>
    <p><span>Musik</span><br>Brad Mehldau - Blackbird (cover)</p>
  </div>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  function copyTextFauzi() {
    const targetElement = document.getElementById("bank-fauzi");
    const textToCopy = targetElement.textContent
      .replace(/\s+/g, " ")
      .trim();
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(textToCopy);

    const myButton = document.getElementById("copy-fauzi")
    myButton.disabled = true;
    targetElement.textContent = "Tersalin!";

    setTimeout(() => {
    myButton.disabled = false;
    targetElement.textContent = "4970646847";
    }, 1000);
  };
</script>
<script is:inline>
  function copyTextNabila() {
    const targetElement = document.getElementById("bank-nabila");
    const textToCopy = targetElement.textContent
      .replace(/\s+/g, " ")
      .trim();
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(textToCopy);
    const myButton = document.getElementById("copy-nabila")
    myButton.disabled = true;
    targetElement.textContent = "Tersalin!";

    setTimeout(() => {
    myButton.disabled = false;
    targetElement.textContent = "1310016137079";
    }, 1000);
  };
</script>
